title.title: July 21, 13:25 hours - Incidents on London Underground

texts: We are responding to reports of incidents at Warren Street and Oval Underground stations.
There are no reports of any casualties at this stage.
We have suspended the Bakerloo, Piccadilly, Hammersmith & City, Victoria and Northern lines.
